description:
Danny welcomes Cameran Eubanks-Wimberly, formerly of Southern Charm, to talk about stepping away from the show, her new book, The Real World, and more. After the chat, Danny welcomes SNL's Heidi Gardner to talk all things Housewives. They discuss Margaret's remodel, the Meredith/Rihanna text, and Heidi advocates for Elizabeth Vargas on Real Housewives of Orange County!


Cameran Interview: 6:00ish

Heidi Gardner Housewives Chat: 35:10ish
